{"tid":1242423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於公屋地址選票問題","createTime":"2019-06-19T04:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T06:34:41.000Z","uid":133121,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e460b77df9b3f8a011a81c06a5920e7640102a3c","tid":1242423,"uid":133121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"本身係住公屋既，之後搬左出去住，媽就係公屋個邊cut左我個名，而家就反左公屋住，甘而家因為投票要地址，我而係公屋戶無名，要住址證明，我怕到時比人捉"},{"pid":"3df3272e4a72cb254adfe7bcf254925c48585d0e","tid":1242423,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:02:16.000Z","msg":"公屋冇名而住, 你全家犯撚晒法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e0d70908573cf3060787e71131bc387e08793c","tid":1242423,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"咁你平時啲信 去邊收？"},{"pid":"34283b4f9ea7d17de6ca2c4b16b7934b3e47a4a1","tid":1242423,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2bd644746e30ef92ef02592c19b76739720878","tid":1242423,"uid":133121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df3272e4a72cb254adfe7bcf254925c48585d0e","tid":1242423,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:02:16.000Z","msg":"公屋冇名而住, 你全家犯撚晒法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:04:54.000Z","msg":"我之前有問過想加反名，應該叫房委，佢地唔比加名，我都係想投票姐，姐係無得投票"},{"pid":"c06bfd83b9ab5d526efa7e6698ac2dd641d60c52","tid":1242423,"uid":133121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e0d70908573cf3060787e71131bc387e08793c","tid":1242423,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"咁你平時啲信 去邊收？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"其實地址都係公屋，無改過"},{"pid":"9f2ac1dce6c1958afe7e4c3759972003ee9b8fd4","tid":1242423,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:05:48.000Z","msg":"咁你咪